Senator MCCAIN. Ms. White, I want to thank you again for being 
here  today.  In  your  statement  you  say  you  were  able  to  pass  17 
drug tests both in and out of competition while utilizing prohibited 
performance-enhancing  substances.  Is  it  just  that  they  were  not 
