I thank the witnesses. We will be introducing legislation with our 
friends  on  the  House  side  today  to  hopefully  address  some  of  this 
issue.  We  thank  you  for  being  here  and  thank  you  for  all  you  do. 

This hearing is adjourned. 
[Whereupon, at 10:57 a.m., the Committee was adjourned.]

